<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>File Upload</title>
    <style>
        div {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        div:first-child {
            background-color: lightpink;
        }

        div:nth-child(2) {
            background-color: lightyellow;
        }

        div:last-child {
            background-color: lightblue;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div>
        <h2>하나의 인풋에 하나의 파일 업로드</h2>
        <form action="/upload/single" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="제목"><br>
            <input type="file" name="single" id="single"><br>
            <button type="submit">업로드</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h2>하나의 인풋에 여러 개의 파일 업로드</h2>
        <form action="/upload/array" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="제목"><br>
            <input type="file" name="array" id="array" multiple><br>
            <button type="submit">업로드</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h2>여러 인풋에 여러 개의 파일 업로드</h2>
        <form action="/upload/fields" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="제목1"><br>
            <input type="file" name="fields1" id="fields1"><br>
            <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="제목2"><br>
            <input type="file" name="fields2" id="fields2" multiple><br>
            <button type="submit">업로드</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>

</html>